That(deserialized.getSetterValue()).isEqualTo(\\\"from setter\\\");\\n        assertThat(deserialized.fieldValue).isEqualTo(\\\"from field\\\");\\n    }\\n\\n    @Test\\n    void populatesDocumentIdAnnotatedSetters() throws Exception {\\n        try (Firestore firestore = newFirestore()) {\\n            DocumentReference documentReference = firestore.document(\\\"messages/message-one\\\");\\n\\n            PojoBeanMapperDocumentIdStringSetterBean stringSetterBean =\\n                    CustomClassMapper.convertToCustomClass(\\n                            Collections.emptyMap(),\\n                            PojoBeanMapperDocumentIdStringSetterBean.class,\\n                            documentReference);\\n            PojoBeanMapperDocumentIdReferenceSetterBean referenceSetterBean =\\n                    CustomClassMapper.convertToCustomClass(\\n                            Collections.emptyMap(),\\n                            PojoBeanMapperDocumentIdReferenceSetterBean.class,\\n                            documentReference);\\n\\n            assertThat(stringSetterBean.getDocumentId()).isEqualTo(\\\"message-one\\\");\\n            assertThat(referenceSetterBean.getDocumentReference()).isSameAs(documentReference);\\n        }\\n    }\\n\\n    @Test\\n    void populatesDocumentIdAnnotatedFields() throws Exception {\\n        try (Firestore firestore = newFirestore()) {\\n            DocumentReference documentReference = firestore.document(\\\"messages/message-two\\\");\\n\\n            PojoBeanMapperDocumentIdStringFieldBean stringFieldBean =\\n                    CustomClassMapper.convertToCustomClass(\\n                            Collections.emptyMap(),\\n                            PojoBeanMapperDocumentIdStringFieldBean.class,\\n                            documentReference);\\n            PojoBeanMapperDocumentIdReferenceFieldBean referenceFieldBean =\\n                    CustomClassMapper.convertToCustomClass(\\n                            Collections.emptyMap(),\\n                            PojoBeanMapperDocumentIdReferenceFieldBean.class,\\n                            documentReference);\\n\\n            assertThat(stringFieldBean.documentId).isEqualTo(\\\"message-two\\\");\\n            assertThat(referenceFieldBean.documentReference).isSameAs(documentReference);\\n        }\\n    }\\n\\n    private static Firestore newFirestore() {\\n        return FirestoreOptions.newBuilder()\\n                .setProjectId(\\\"native-image-test-project\\\")\\n                .setEmulatorHost(\\\"localhost:8080\\\")\\n                .build()\\n                .getService();\\n    }\\n\\n    @SuppressWarnings(\\\"unchecked\\\")\\n    private static Map<String, Object> asMap(Object value) {\\n        assertThat(value).isInstanceOf(Map.class);\\n        return (Map<String, Object>) value;\\n    }\\n}\\n\\nclass PojoBeanMapperSerializationBean {\\n    public String fieldValue;\\n    private String getterValue;\\n\\n    public PojoBeanMapperSerializationBean() {\\n    }\\n\\n    PojoBeanMapperSerializationBean(String getterValue, String fieldValue) {\\n        this.getterValue = getterValue;\\n        this.fieldValue = fieldValue;\\n    }\\n\\n    public String getGetterValue() {\\n        return getterValue;\\n    }\\n}\\n\\nclass PojoBeanMapperDeserializationBean {\\n    public String fieldValue;\\n    private String setterValue;\\n\\n    public PojoBeanMapperDeserializationBean() {\\n    }\\n\\n    public String getSetterValue() {\\n        return setterValue;\\n    }\\n\\n    public void setSetterValue(String setterValue) {\\n        this.setterValue = setterValue;\\n    }\\n}\\n\\nclass PojoBeanMapperDocumentIdStringSetterBean {\\n    private String documentId;\\n\\n    public PojoBeanMapperDocumentIdStringSetterBean() {\\n    }\\n\\n    @DocumentId\\n    public String getDocumentId() {\\n        return documentId;\\n    }\\n\\n    public void setDocumentId(String documentId) {\\n        this.documentId = documentId;\\n    }\\n}\\n\\nclass PojoBeanMapperDocumentIdReferenceSetterBean {\\n    private DocumentReference documentReference;\\n\\n    public PojoBeanMapperDocumentIdReferenceSetterBean() {\\n    }\\n\\n    @DocumentId\\n    public DocumentReference getDocumentReference() {\\n        return documentReference;\\n    }\\n\\n    public void setDocumentReference(DocumentReference documentReference) {\\n        this.documentReference = documentReference;\\n    }\\n}\\n\\nclass PojoBeanMapperDocumentIdStringFieldBean {\\n    @DocumentId public String documentId;\\n\\n    public PojoBeanMapperDocumentIdStringFieldBean() {\\n    }\\n}\\n\\nclass PojoBeanMapperDocumentIdReferenceFieldBean {\\n    @DocumentId public DocumentReference documentReference;\\n\\n    public PojoBeanMapperDocumentIdReferenceFieldBean() {\\n    }\\n}\\n\"}\nhuman-intervention-logs/com.google.cloud:google-cloud-firestore:3.31.6/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-03T16-53-10-611204Z.log:3334:[recv] {\"type\": \"turn_end\", \"message\": {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"thinking\", \"thinking\": \"\", \"thinkingSignature\": \"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"rs_0e16c4517a93d10c0169f77d0b0674819f90533a5c0a624fd2\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"reasoning\\\",\\\"encrypted_content\\\":\\\"gAAAAABp930eRbz4JcPmS-m2Hw_sQ5MQ-LNs8-SFeinxasxkivPZz-BdVibdhPx0uSx_O2KQBdzRxG6mz1QjDv0ZDwnAb1cXJ71prY9S6e4tODIJRXBfXKXDHvjSu6MwLJQJVBQ9sEMi5ChHf38QRSi6T4nUBze6JahFV_xneG4F2swdbM9AtsMQzPM8N4ajOo9ZAyFnVmBV_-uDX3VVCQtwk6gPVwdPRqWdUR1LZoQa1EzQAJnGdqVXClWPEuVQKUQsaV2HFYNzCzzdb1-iYINkbezs6gQF0Qgjfy3iSP71EQr8g98FtE-bSy8dDN6IxJumJ5UoGOe1cQsvs2Bu3qhJNnquQSZ2bnDuTvqpZII21skgaYOIiJKdt099Kqm1nu1a0pqiMZjBTvfblfer_0SEyMY8a-ysiijdxvLL6Lzhl2rn_wveSzS_1C_LHz2s8oEXrPzlc_RQPRiyakNo5NS6vM3DFJSllMlHURgipasUSFq5kO35G7iBzxQWINYsAEVkSGeHwd_zuUmDuDFRdJusxb-nJgXYm7E9p2CDu6D--ullMElImZEYO9Ts_Wz94N9A3flbUhBsJkWyqeXfnKpnMtIdfDg6XE0HBTIgWhwkAZVQpe15-uHSb0lVhePd5M8ImcdpMIVkpWIfY0wojWg9g8peiDdoB-8Lm0VLkewwT98LtXh65wMuwGcOltzhVkDh8xCVHrxYQZCd3ZAmxN9iRc3UiBOmvrbfOVEx30y